      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "his people into the San Bernardino Valley. Long before we would be",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -4,
          "y_px": -98.562
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-4",
        "text": "Before the arrival of European settlers. Before Santos Manuel led",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 1,
          "y_px": -125.138
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-6",
        "text": "called the San Manuel Band of Mission Indians, our Tribe had a name.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -1,
          "y_px": -75.868
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "It echoed across the highlands, passes, valleys and mountains.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": -3.611
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "It was not the name we adopted to survive a hostile world.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 20.06
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "It was not attached to any foreign concept, like “Mission Indians.”",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 43.612
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "It was not given to us by others, so it could never be taken away.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 67.307
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "This name was our own, spoken in our language and rooted in our traditions.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 114.649
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "Today, its spirit lives on in all of us. It is forever part of our history.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 161.991
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "It is the heart and soul of our sovereignty. It is why we must reclaim",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 185.567
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "our namesake for our ancestors and the generations to come.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 10
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 0,
          "y_px": 209.262
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
